      "parameters": {
        "promptType": "define",
        "text": "=",
        "options": {
          "systemMessage": "=Real Estate AI Agents before generating the caption\n\nThis is my niche for the sentences you create AI Agents\n\nWrite a short motivational caption that always starts with: POV:\n\nSpeak directly to the reader using \u201cyou.\u201d\nMake the first half about a moment of freedom, rest, or success.\nMake the second half about what was achieved in [your niche] while they weren\u2019t working.\n\nUse numbers when possible (e.g. 5K views, 10 sales, 3 clients).\n\nRules:\n\nMax 90 characters total\n\nMax 45 characters per line\n\nDo NOT use line breaks or newline characters\n\nDo NOT use quotation marks\n\nDo NOT use emojis, hashtags, or filler words\n\nOutput as a single plain text string \u2014 no formatting\n\nExamples:\n\nPOV: You relaxed all day and still gained 3 new clients in [your niche]\n\nPOV: You skipped the gym and made 5 sales in [your niche]\n\nPOV: You went out and your blog hit 10K views in [your niche]\n\nNow write the caption:\n\nFormat:\nPOV: You [freedom/success] while your [system/process] got [result] in [your niche]"
        }
      },
